API(Application Programming Interface)- is way we expose our resources to the client
(web or mobile app) through endpoints.

Restful APIs - Representational State Transfer defines rules for client-sever communication over the internet.
This make our application fast, scalable, Reliable, easy to understand and change

Resources are objects in our application, They are accessed through the Url(web address) and the URL must follow
a specific pattern

INSTALLATION WALKOUT for restful API
======================================
* pipenv install djangorestframework
* Add to list of INSTALLED APPS

Serializer defines the fields to be shown to the user because some information's are sensitive e.g date_of_death

Serializer is how we convert a Python Object to JSON Format